## Risks & Tradeoffs
- Increased operational complexity
- Bureaucratic overhead
- Potential contributor discouragement if advancement is unclear
- Risk of hierarchy formation
- Governance capture risks
- Difficulty standardizing across diverse projects

---

## Failure Conditions
The framework may fail if:
- Advancement criteria are inconsistent
- Governance lacks transparency
- Mentorship systems are weak
- Recognition systems are absent
- Contributors feel excluded
- Operational expectations are unclear
- Maintainers become centralized gatekeepers

